<template>

</template>

<script>
import store from '@/store';
import { mapGetters } from 'vuex';
export default {
  name: 'Room',
  computed: {
    ...mapGetters(['UserInfo', "Token"])
  },
  data() {
    return
    { RoomId: undefined }
  },
  created() {

    this.RoomId = this.$route.query.RoomId;
  },
  methods: {
    // 得到自习室详情接口
    async GetRoomApi() {
      let { Data: { Items, TotalCount } } = await this.$Post("/Room/List", {});
      this.RoomList = Items;

    },
  }
}
</script>
